{"article_id":"w7s7X8pUctN3ClBy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Trump Says","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"More Testing Makes U.S. 'Look Bad , '","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"But Its Availability Remains A Concern","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"The coronavirus has in recent days edged closer to President Trump .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"At least two White House aides","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"who 've been in proximity to the president and the vice president","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"have tested positive for COVID-19 .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Because of that ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"three key members of the Trump administration 's pandemic response team are quarantining themselves :","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Drs . Robert Redfield , Stephen Hahn and Anthony Fauci .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Redfield is head of the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Hahn heads up the Food and Drug Administration","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"and Fauci is director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"and is the nation 's top infectious disease expert .","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"All three , plus the assistant secretary for health , Dr. Brett Giroir , are slated to testify before a key Senate committee Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"The hearing ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"which is ironically titled `` COVID-19 : Safely Getting Back to Work and Back to School , ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"will now be done via video conference .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"The chair of that committee , Tennessee Republican Lamar Alexander , is also self-quarantining .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"His office announced Sunday night","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that a member of the staff tested positive for COVID-19 .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Alexander will chair Tuesday 's hearing from Tennessee .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"In recent days , Alexander has said","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that the coronavirus testing","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"the United States has done so far","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"is `` not nearly enough , ''","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and `` there is no safe path forward","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to combat the novel coronavirus","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"without adequate testing . ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Trump has touted the overall number of tests","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that have been conducted in the country","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"- now more than 8 million .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"But at times he 's read a different message in them .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"`` If we did very little testing ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"[ America ] would n't have the most cases , ''","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Trump said Wednesday .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"`` So , in a way ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"by doing all of this testing ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"we make ourselves look bad . ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"And Trump 's reservations about testing appear to be rooted in politics .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Trump said Friday","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"he believes","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"some Democrats hope","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"the economy does n't bounce back .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"`` I will tell you ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"you look at some cases ,","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"some people think","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"they 're doing it for politics , ''","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"Trump said on Fox News Channel .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"`` Here we go again .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"But they think","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"they 're doing it","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"because it 'll hurt me ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"the longer it takes to - hurt me in the election ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"the longer it takes to open up . ''","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"But Trump 's focus on how the pandemic makes him and the nation look","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"does n't get the country closer to being prepared and able to live with the coronavirus .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"`` We have to figure out how to live with this virus ,","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"and that 's what we 're not doing , ''","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"Michael Osterholm , director of the Center for Infectious Disease Research and Policy at the University of Minnesota , said on NBC 's Meet the Press Sunday .","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"On the White House schedule Monday :","depth":4},{"id":61,"text":"a press briefing about testing .","depth":4},{"id":62,"text":"1 . Climbing coronavirus death toll :","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"The confirmed number of Americans","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"who have now died from the coronavirus","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"is about 80,000 .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"At a rate of 1,000 to 2,000 deaths per day , the U.S. would surpass 100,000 deaths from COVID-19 between May 21 and May 31 .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"The country 's curve has plateaued ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"but it appears to have a long tail .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"And that flattening is masked by New York and New Jersey 's daily new cases","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"coming down ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"because new cases are on the rise in other places .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"2 . Those CDC guidelines","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"for reopening :","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"If you 're wondering","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"why","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"- despite access to some of the top scientists in the world -","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"there have n't been clearer and more detailed reopening guidelines for states , businesses and religious institutions","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"coming from the federal government ,","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"you 're not alone .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"And now we know why :","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"The White House buried them .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"The guidelines from the CDC were shelved ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"the AP reported .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Following the publication of the report ,","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"CDC Director Redfield issued a statement","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"that appeared to run contrary to his published internal emails .","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"He took responsibility","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"and said","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"the document was `` shared prematurely ,","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"'' `` was in draft form","depth":17},{"id":91,"text":"and had not been vetted through the interagency review process . ''","depth":17},{"id":92,"text":"Because of that ,","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"Redfield added ,","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"he `` was not yet comfortable releasing a final work product . ''","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"Will the CDC release new guidelines at some point","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"now that this is out there ?","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"3 . Will the White House push for another relief package","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"- or not ?","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"White House economic adviser Kevin Hassett said on CNN 's State of the Union Sunday","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"that another relief package would be `` premature ''","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"given the others","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"that have already passed","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"and trillions total in aid .","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"`` We think","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"that we have a little moment , the luxury of a moment ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"to learn about what 's going on","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"so that the next step","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"that we take","depth":16},{"id":109,"text":"can be prudent . ''","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"Luxury of a moment ?","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"The country on Friday hit its highest unemployment rate , 14.7 % , since the Great Depression ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"most economists think","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"that number is actually higher ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and Americans lost a whopping 20 million jobs","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"- in one month .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"4 . U.S. Supreme Court on religious freedom , Trump 's financial records and faithless electors :","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"People may be home ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"but the Supreme Court justices are working","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"- even if remotely .","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"On Monday , the court considers arguments","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"about whether lay teachers at parochial schools are protected from discrimination","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"or whether the schools can have carte blanche","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"in hiring and firing .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"On Tuesday , it 's Trump 's financial records","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"and whether Congress has the power","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"to subpoena records from when before Trump was president","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"- and whether those can be used in a potential criminal investigation .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Law","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"Toilet Flush Heard During Supreme Court 's Conference Call","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"Toilet Flush Heard During Supreme Court 's Conference Call","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"Listen ·","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"0:25","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"0:25","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"On Wednesday , the quirky Electoral College system sees a challenge .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Electors are actually people ,","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and sometimes they do n't go the way","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"their state voted .","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"The court considers","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"whether that 's OK .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"For everyone 's sake , let 's hope","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"those mute buttons are working better this week , especially close to any toilets .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"5 . Will Bright be reinstated ?","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"Rick Bright , the former director of the Biomedical Advanced Research and Development Authority , a key agency in vaccine development , will testify before a House committee Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"It comes","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"after he filed a whistleblower complaint against the Trump administration","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"for being dismissed from his position ,","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"he says ,","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"for sounding alarms about the coronavirus early on","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"and expressing opposition to unproven treatments","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"favored by Trump .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"Bright 's lawyers say","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"the Office of Special Counsel has made a determination","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"that he was dismissed for retaliation","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"and should be temporarily reinstated","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"while the office investigates .","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"Trump has ignored the same office 's recommendations before ,","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"but Bright 's case will continue to be in the public eye , especially this week -","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"and as the pandemic fallout continues .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"`` It would have been bad even with the best of governments .","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"It has been an absolute chaotic disaster","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"when that mindset","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"- of 'what 's in it for me ' and 'to heck with everybody else ' -","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"when that mindset is operationalized in our government . ''","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"Former President Barack Obama on the Trump administration 's coronavirus response .","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"The comments were revealed in a leaked recording","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"of Obama","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"speaking to a group of members of his administration .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":337,"left":171,"right":336,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":171,"left":0,"right":170,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":170,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":336,"left":227,"right":335,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":227,"left":189,"right":226,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":185,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":181,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":3,"right":180,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":173,"right":179,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":173,"left":172,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":172,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":175,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":7,"right":174,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":174,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":10,"right":177,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":11,"right":176,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":176,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":184,"left":14,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":182,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":182,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":187,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":18,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":1